603
00:50:45,108 --> 00:50:47,702
You are on a strange journey
to redemption, Mr. Devine.

604
00:50:47,778 --> 00:50:50,406
And a very long one, Mrs. Clark.

605
00:50:54,217 --> 00:50:56,344
